#: ../../../release_details/9.5/breaking-change-remove-nlohmann-json-from-public-API.md:1
msgid "Remove usage of the nlohmannjson library from public facing API"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/breaking-change-remove-nlohmann-json-from-public-API.md:3
msgid ""
"The `nlohmann::json vtkAbstractArray::SerializeValues()` method is now "
"removed as the public exposure of VTK's vendored `nlohmannjson` library "
"caused difficulty for downstream projects that link to a different "
"nlohmannjson."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/breaking-change-remove-nlohmann-json-from-public-API.md:6
msgid ""
"These methods were added in [vtk/vtk!11163](https://gitlab.kitware.com/vtk/"
"vtk/-/merge_requests/11163) which was released in 9.4. That merge request "
"has now been reverted. These methods are removed (instead of deprecation) "
"because deprecation would prevent fixing the problem."
msgstr ""
